      <title>全球科技战升级，英伟达遭中国调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-targets-nvidia-for-potential-breaches-of-anti-monopoly-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国政府加大制裁力度之际，中国已对英伟达公司展开调查，怀疑这家美国芯片制造商在 2020 年的一项交易中违反了反垄断法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/china-targets-nvidia-for-potential-breaches-of-anti-monopoly-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 11:46:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
